  "comments": "Donated by the Franklin Mint in 1975.  Moved to the current location in 1999.   People listed are those visible June 20, 2022.  Many of the plaques are missing or damaged.  One was covered by a planter.  Preference given here to likenesses of those least represented in the database as of 7/4/2022.",
